What sets Perplexity apart?

With so many AI tools out there, we understand it can be tough to choose the right one for you. Today, we'll share how Perplexity
stands out from other search engines and AI tools.




We focus on search

Ask any question, and we'll curate the most relevant, high-quality information from across the web and craft a comprehensive,
easy-to-understand response just for you.




Transparency is key

We believe in trust and accuracy. That's why every Perplexity answer comes with clear citations, linking you directly to the
sources we used. Curious about where we found our information? Click the source tab and see for yourself.
Other tools give you black-box answers. Perplexity gives you context.
 


Up-to-date information

Our real-time access to the web means your answers are always current. Whether it's breaking news or the latest research, you'll
get the most recent information available with Perplexity.



Discover more with follow-up questions

After every answer, we generate three follow-up questions to help you explore further. Our fast, comprehensive answers encourage
curiosity and deeper investigation.
 


Search beyond words

Sometimes, an image or video does the job better than text. That's why our answers include visuals that make your search
experience richer and more intuitive.
 

